metadata.name: Bluechip WC #1
metadata.description:
BlueChip NFT World Cup is a world cup themed social game for NFT enthusiasts, which lets you share the total prize pool (if you HOLD the winning countryâ€™s NFT at the end of the tournament), as you support your favourite national team during this coming world cup that is held in Qatar. Each art will pay tribute to a famous NFT.

Click into [https://www.bluechipnftwc.wtf/](https://www.bluechipnftwc.wtf/) and check out the total Prize Pool daily!
Secondary sales are set to 10% creator fee as it contributes to the total Prize Pool.
